module.exports = dot

/**
 * Calculates the dot product of two vec4's
 *
 * @param {vec4} a the first operand
 * @param {vec4} b the second operand
 * @returns {Number} dot product of a and b
 */
function dot (a, b) {
  return a[0] * b[0] + a[1] * b[1] + a[2] * b[2] + a[3] * b[3]
}
